                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                langAttribute="none"
                                text="&lt;p>Linda Ray is Senior Vice President, Chief Information Officer,&amp;nbsp;responsible for AbbVie’s technology systems and data assets, focused on enabling business growth and&amp;nbsp;operational effectiveness&amp;nbsp;priorities.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Ms. Ray has more than 30 years of diverse experience. She joined AbbVie in 2017 and most recently served as Senior Vice President, Business Technology Solutions. Prior to&amp;nbsp;joining AbbVie, Ms. Ray held technology roles of increasing responsibility at W.W. Grainger, and also has a background in human resources.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Ms. Ray holds a bachelor’s degree in communication and a master’s degree in organizational communication from the University of Colorado. She also holds&amp;nbsp;a master’s degree in business administration from William E. Simon Graduate&amp;nbsp;School of Business Administration, University of Rochester – New York.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
